OL,3,CTwo West Country zoos up for sale amid
OL,4,Cfinancial difficulties, owners say
OL,6,FThe owner of Newquay Zoo has confirmed
OL,7,Fit's up for sale after facing
OL,8,Ffinancial difficulties, its owner has
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe announcement that the zoo, home to
OL,12,Faround 850 animals, is for sale
OL,13,Ffollows confirmation on Wednesday 1
OL,14,FOctober that its sister site, Paignton
OL,15,FZoo is on the market.
OL,17,FConservation charity Wild Planet
OL,18,FTrust, which manages both zoos, said
OL,19,Fit is "exploring all avenues" to try
OL,20,Fand protect the long-term future of
OL,21,Fboth attractions.
