OL,6,FStaff there added that both zoos
OL,7,Fremain open and will continue to
OL,8,Fwelcome visitors through the process.
OL,10,FStephen Kings, Interim Chief Executive
OL,11,Fat Wild Planet Trust, said: "We're
OL,12,Fexploring all avenues to secure the
OL,13,Ffuture of both Paignton Zoo and
OL,14,FNewquay Zoo for the next century and
OL,15,Fbeyond.
