OL,3,CTwo West Country zoos up for sale amid
OL,4,Cfinancial difficulties, owners say
OL,6,F"Like many charities, we've faced
OL,7,Frising costs and global challenges,
OL,8,Fand we've already made difficult but
OL,9,Fnecessary internal changes. Now we're
OL,10,Flooking at every option to ensure we
OL,11,Fdon't just survive, but flourish."
OL,13,FThe Trust says it has received
OL,14,Fexpressions of interest from across
OL,15,Fthe UK and Europe, though discussions
OL,16,Fremain at a very early stage.
