OL,6,FStephen Kings added: "There have been
OL,7,Fconversations with potential investors
OL,8,Fand interested parties, which is very
OL,9,Fencouraging. We are cautiously
OL,10,Foptimistic. But I have to emphasise
OL,11,Fthat these are very, very early days."
OL,13,FThe trust says visitor numbers have
OL,14,Fbeen "holding steady" since the
OL,15,Fannouncement.
