OL,3,CTwo West Country zoos up for sale amid
OL,4,Cfinancial difficulties, owners say
OL,6,F"These zoos belong to the community `
OL,7,Fthey always have. People are proud of
OL,8,Fboth zoos, and the response we've
OL,9,Freceived this past week has been truly
OL,10,Fhumbling. It has only strengthened our
OL,11,Fresolve to find the right solution for
OL,12,Fthe future," Stephen Kings continued.
OL,14,FIn July 2024 the Wild Planet Trust
OL,15,Fannounced a number of redundancies at
OL,16,FPaignton Zoo in Devon and Newquay Zoo
OL,17,Fin Cornwall. At the time, it said
OL,18,Foperational costs for both zoos
OL,19,Famounted to #1 million per month.
